{
  "stem": "17374.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 214.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And as my brother-in-law didn't want to stay there, we applied to visa for Venezuela, I think.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But we find out that Leo got some cousin in Paris.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And they went first, to Paris, and then we joined, and then we been in Paris.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And that's when Anna was born, in [FRENCH] hospital.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Yes, it was a such experience for me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I didn't know what it mean to be pregnant.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I didn't know what to be mother.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I didn't know language.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And it-- food wasn't-- wasn't opened.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "You couldn't go to shop to buy milk or anything.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "We have special cart for mother who were feeding babies.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And I went to this with the cart.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I put the cart, and I took them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Later on, they said to my sister, poor, poor young woman-- she's deaf and dumb-- because I didn't know French.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And I-- I have to find out in Paris.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "We have very little.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "First, we had a big apartment, what his cousin let him have it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "But I want to be with my sister, and they didn't know that his cousin, who live in Paris, [INAUDIBLE] my sister.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we have-- my brother, [INAUDIBLE], bought-- pay him, not bought-- he paid him money to get to some apartment at a flat, right?",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was one room and a kitchen, nothing more, very tiny, very small.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My sister had the baby five weeks before me, a baby boy.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She was in private hospital, and she was a very hard labor.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, well, I went to the Lafayette to buy a big teddy bear.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I went to the hospital.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My tummy is already big, and they just thought that I'm going to have a baby.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That was fun.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then five week after, I went to the [FRENCH] hospital.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
